{"tid":280402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲港少女被通緝赴台後失蹤 時代力量：人權組織照顧","createTime":"2017-06-12T05:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T17:30:54.000Z","uid":13663,"like":42,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc8d0d19675b0a514b7a50e7d369a6d217ad5bf6","tid":280402,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"民進黨與時代力量立委發起組成「台灣國會關注香港民主連線」，表達台灣社會關注香港民主化，今天上午舉行成立茶會，並邀請香港立法會議員朱凱廸、香港眾志羅冠聰、人民力量陳志全，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒以及周永康等出席。時代力量黨主席黃國昌首次透露，參與旺角騷亂而被控暴動罪的18歲香港女子李倩怡的行蹤，目前她正身處台灣，獲人權組織照顧，連線成立後，時代力量會推動在立法院，修改港澳關係條例，給予港人政治庇護。<br />\n<br />\n涉及去年旺角騷亂被控暴動罪的18歲少女李倩怡，原定於今年1月中提訊，但她缺席聆訊，法庭即時發出通緝令。早前有報道指，李已往台灣尋求政治庇護。陸委會港澳處長杜嘉芬表示，目前為止，李倩怡沒有向陸委會申請庇護，依照條例，若果收到求助，會提供必要協助。<br />\n<br />\n黃國昌在會上稱，香港回歸中國20周年，外界清楚看到港人為爭取真正自由、建立民主制度所做的努力，但北京政府仍不斷打壓，讓香港人權與自由都遭限縮，因此希望邀集台灣跨黨派立委，未來能共同關注、支持香港爭取民主，台港議員也能有進一步交流，在青年、土地發展等議題上，彼此提供經驗、作為借鏡。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志立法會議員羅冠聰表示，香港問題很需要國際關注與支持，台灣一直都是香港盟友，台港都要面對來自中國威權政府、對人權議題的挑戰和壓力，像是李明哲事件和銅鑼灣書店事件，台港要互相扶持協助，一起追求人權與民主自由普世價值。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒也說，在北京政府壓逼下，香港的一國兩制已經變成一國1.5制，現在香港不太能談論香港民主問題，但正因如此，港台才需要有更多交流，感謝台灣有這麼多立委支持香港。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"fe96ed3767972a9fb7f0c781fceefddb9324a7bc","tid":280402,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1802813468100055d94d877f96a7ce552e63a4c1","tid":280402,"uid":18391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6268d8d31386f42658cd3e45a467762d264af794","tid":280402,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe74022bc9150bb58bebdc2650ab050686c961fb","tid":280402,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f35eaffbe4474d906b85628a0b7721107ad45ca","tid":280402,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:41:40.000Z","msg":"豬隊友"},{"pid":"dd331d593b91f40e3286bebee3339ebfa37c261b","tid":280402,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215cab975a96fdcd921c66740be8bc40079ddfb8","tid":280402,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009f678a379d3d9fab5bb105c2d7e6df1dbb8d0a","tid":280402,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"79f25d981e1bf8558e9466d7796b3de8cde12baf","tid":280402,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"請代為好好照顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5914732e0b35e496ad7843086a8ee09e241fe4","tid":280402,"uid":11484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"代表香港人多謝你"},{"pid":"045f19ecbab5056acf10e68685731196173fe680","tid":280402,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323db948d41b175e92e266327c30817e8fb4bd26","tid":280402,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6193ad44dc334527e6f074856c4c427465d3022","tid":280402,"uid":29034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"等班熱狗仲想屈鳩人做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62420b715783651fd98426324f3212d660c4a3bb","tid":280402,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等班熱狗仲想屈鳩人做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd3158028c5d012a35d7963b519b70248b0769b","tid":280402,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7389dc4a9796ba3b0985288f6e2e2f4270da49e","tid":280402,"uid":29034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>等班熱狗仲想屈鳩人做雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係呢？得佢地而家咁撚屎忽痕要靠傳呢啲謠言掩蓋佢地幾柒，鋒頭又故意指向本民青，唔係要估邊個啊？講呢句製造熱狗被迫害既假象啊"},{"pid":"3fe48be313b0b6cb0c488ab5f2d819ba273406c4","tid":280402,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd7066aaedad12ae24e703121f15e1c9936db52e","tid":280402,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代力量澄清 從未接觸過涉旺角騷亂少女</span></span><br 